Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 同行者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是里维拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险者们建造出来的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好..好贵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这砥石居然要13000瓦利斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这破破烂烂的包居然要价20000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太无法无天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要的话我也不强求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的旅馆也贵得吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们才在森林里露营
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？上神大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 什么时候跑那去了..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是酒馆里的小屁孩菜鸟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子..那时候居然..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你在说什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 摩多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然认识剑姬么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:03:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮人怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是逊暴了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 味道很好闻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道贝尔会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种奸商镇子里买那种东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金钱观念太缺乏了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 支援者小姐不也买了那个背包吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是回到地面的必需品 我才硬着头皮买的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我的必需品啊 是少女的风雅之趣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 你也不喜欢有汗臭味的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？我倒是从来没考虑过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫斯缇雅大人 我们一会正打算去泡澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去 要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请务必带上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊？荷米斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 回营地之后能占用你一些时间么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特 实在是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运送解毒剂这种麻烦事 为啥要叫我去..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你 看来明天所有人都能出发回地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算以2班分头行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你将跟随先头部队..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么兔子小鬼在这里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？啊 发生了各种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种事是什么意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 荷米斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说您要单独找我 所以就跟来了..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可为什么要上树呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往下看吧 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我完胜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟谁较劲呢 赫斯缇雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子们在洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然必须来偷窥一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫“当然”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以做这种事啦 荷米斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷窥是男人的浪漫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷窥是男人的浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪浪浪浪浪漫啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧 荷米斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？是英雄愿望君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么？你也来洗澡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸上天真老实 其实很有两下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个..那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在做什么啊？贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔 你这个家伙还真是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对..对不起！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？这里是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水声？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对..对不起！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 来龙去脉我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必再介意此事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯原谅我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怀疑我是在撒谎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然谦虚是美德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可千万不要贬低自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的坏习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在才说有些晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还是要谢谢你特地赶来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还劳烦你跑来这种地方..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迟早准备要来一趟这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了给她们献花 我时不时会跟米娅阿姨请假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉小姐 这里是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我所属眷族的同伴们的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去 我们陷入了敌对眷族在地下城中设下的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我之外的队员全都被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生 愿意听我说说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工会的黑名单上有我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我毁灭了一整个敌对的眷族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀 偷袭 设伏..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了帮同伴们报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所不用其极 任凭恨意驱使..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我力尽而竭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了对所有人的报复之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒在一条寂寥黑暗的后巷里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于犯下愚行的我而言 如此下场本是罪有应得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被丰饶的女主人收留..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娅阿姨她在得知一切的情况下仍接纳了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起让你听到些丑恶之事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 我是个不知羞耻而蛮横无比的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辜负了克朗尼先生对我的信赖..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要贬低自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是..被你反将一军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 我太不知天高地厚了..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克朗尼先生 你很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一位值得尊敬的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 火气不小啊 摩多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小鬼 到底耍了什么把戏 竟能来到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧那趾高气昂的德行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你嫉妒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也说不得别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂妄的菜鸟 刚刚升级就马上来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而多少年前就在这里滞留不前的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会成为天大的笑话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险者有冒险者的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须好好教教他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把他一个人引出来..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这兔子小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看谁不好 居然偏偏去偷看艾丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋 我都没法做的事居然让你抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事已经了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为所有的错都算在荷米斯大人头上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好严厉~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 笨蛋亚马逊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 为什么那家伙会在这里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喋喋不休的很烦人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丝小姐也要出发了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为我被分入了先行出发的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你们会跟后续的队伍同行对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那..那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您保重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 贝尔这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要偷窥的话 等到只剩我一人再来就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？上神大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小新秀 女神在我们手上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让她平安回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就独自前来中央树的正东方 一柱水晶之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别以为这样做可以全身而退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样 我可是神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上神大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家的女神大人没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是那种敢伤害神明的孽障啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你要找的是我对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不会让这帮家伙动手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我要跟你一对一单挑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 很简单吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢的人可以任意差遣败家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢的话 你就把全身上下的装备都给我扒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢的话 请把上神大人还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帅气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别会错意了 臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一场将你虐杀致死的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害啊 真的看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 摩多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把这菜鸟的鼻梁给折断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回场内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 赶紧给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是备受期待的新秀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看看他那张脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法道具 哈迪斯头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮啊 亚丝菲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的嗜好还真是恶劣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成对贝尔·克朗尼有仇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是我特有的爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔对人类的丑恶一面所知太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是出于我嗜好还是别的 我都想让他见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他知道人的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过嘛 我不否认这也算一种消遣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他从此一蹶不振的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说明他不是堪当大任的料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？他们好像也察觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个孩子都好耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁这么大胆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔应该就在对面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小小新秀的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管了 给我干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草 拿枪来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面热闹起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我也好想去看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不准无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..你是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敲响12点的钟声..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支..支援者小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我利用了犬人族的嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多亏了赫斯缇雅大人乱用的香水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃尽吧 外法之业 无形鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕 我们的数量稳赢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包围他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 靠近不了贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也真是死性不改呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是偶然吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 能看见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉得到..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带有敌意的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:19:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我剁了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这..臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上神大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子民们 收起你们的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 赫斯缇雅解放神意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的余兴节目就此结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 上神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 为了我让你被人打成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能保护好您 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就告一段落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不祥的摇晃..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是..什么啊？
